  "instructions": [
    "1. Cut the cod into bite-sized pieces and season with salt and pepper.",
    "2. Melt 1 tablespoon of butter in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "3. Add the onion and garlic and cook until softened.",
    "4. Add the flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "5. Gradually add the milk, whisking continuously.",
    "6. Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook until thickened.",
    "7. Add the cheddar cheese and stir until melted.",
    "8. Add the cod to the pot and cook until cooked through.",
    "9. Add the diced potato and cook until tender.",
    "10. Serve hot, garnished with chopped parsley if desired."
